title: Looking for a Duo (Ranked)
body:
I main support and I'm looking to duo with someone who mains or can play ADC 
I'm currently B5.

Add me if you wanna play a game
 
01FallenAngel01

replies.body: If you are looking for a team or duo, feel free to jump into https://discord.gg/Y93kJJN . Give a yell in #general with the @league of legends mention and I am sure you will get many of responses from many players.
